{% endfor %}

## Extensions

Project-specific guidance and accumulated knowledge layer onto skills and agents at runtime via the runtime context loader:

- **Lessons** — `~/Claude/{project}/lessons/*.md`. Authored by `/learn` after retrospectives; inlined into every skill at load.
- **Skill overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/skill_<name>.md`. Inlined into the matching skill at load.
- **Agent overrides** — `~/Claude/{project}/_booping/agent_booping-<name>.md`. Inlined into the matching agent at load.

## Hard rules

- **`/help` never writes files.** If the user needs scaffolding, hand off to `/install`.

